# Original Idea

Web UI chat interface. Heavily research requirements and existing web UI features based on nullclaw and other projects (see ~/src/pag-server/ref-projects/*). Should support all normal expected things: show tool calls, show thinking, stream messages from LLM (including thinking), support slash commands with autocomplete menu and suggestions, etc.

